{"tid":1992042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：防疫措施並非百分百建基於科學","createTime":"2020-04-28T02:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T03:00:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dc32d10c5228ee32e6358c25495eed503c064e5d","tid":1992042,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:00:33.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，不少防疫措施的有效期都在下月7日屆滿，包括內地抵港人士要強制家居檢疫、食肆和其他商業處所的規限，以及限聚令，她相信政府今天未能交代最新安排，但相信很快會有公布，讓大家有準備。林鄭月娥在行政會議前表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">防疫措施要張馳有道，能收能放，形容作出相關決定是非常困難，有如三人拔河，既有公共衛生的考慮，也要顧及措施對經濟影響和市民接受程度，因此作出有關決定，並非百分百建基於科學的決定</span>。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，疫情是會反覆，在疫苗面世和大部份人免疫之前，大家仍要嚴陣以待，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府不會一下子放寬措施，而會逐步放寬，但有需要時，亦要收緊</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283871&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283871%26csid%3D261_341&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5bb8f02b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283871&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ebf6b03fdba51a3bfe3626cee4487eb0ec62d3fc","tid":1992042,"uid":26752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:01:48.000Z","msg":"係咪用終國巫術aka中醫"},{"pid":"398d7758a9c667617bb2b9b676540c857ec56b6a","tid":1992042,"uid":13504,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:02:15.000Z","msg":"建基於政治"},{"pid":"e285ea0521e60202c63d5483fceef68631370afc","tid":1992042,"uid":19527,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"百分之九十九建基政治"},{"pid":"f84857b41978d286310fb49f708c18627a245af6","tid":1992042,"uid":245033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"百份百建基於政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明晒"},{"pid":"172ab637faf822569da5389630a40c9dd8c8c766","tid":1992042,"uid":45910,"like":2,"